response.original_title: Extreme Rising Card Subject To Change
response.overview: December 29th, 2012 :: Extreme Rising presents Card Subject To Change from the Pennsylvania National Guard Armory in Philadelphia, PA, USA. Matches include: • Extreme Rising World Title Tournament Semi Final Match Luke Hawx vs. Stevie Richards • Extreme Rising World Title Tournament Semi Final Match Rhino vs. Devon Storm • Jay Bradley vs. Facade • Balls Mahoney & The Blue Meanie vs. Brian XL & Matt Tremont • Little Guido vs. Papadon • Jerry Lynn vs. Homicide • Best Two Out Of Three Falls Match Bestia 666 vs. El Hijo de Rey Misterio • Steel Cage Match The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) vs. BLKOUT (BLK Jeez & Ruckus) vs. El Dramaticos (Dramatic #1 & Dramatic #2) • Matt Hardy vs. Sabu • Extreme Rising World Title Tournament Finals
